data.html: People Announcements

EnterpriseProperties.Comments: We have compiled important information for you as an employee or a manager on the "My Employment" pages.
EnterpriseProperties.pagesummary: We have compiled important information for you as an employee or a manager on the "My Employment" pages.
EnterpriseProperties.pagecontent:
On these pages you can find documents, guidelines and overall information about your employment at SWEP.

Locate your specific country information in the menu bar to the left.

EnterpriseProperties.pagesummary: The Employee Handbook contains information about your employment at SWEP.
EnterpriseProperties.pagecontent:
The Employee Handbook is for you as a SWEP employee. Here you will find information that is associated to your employment and you can read about different rules and guidelines. Owner of the content is HR at each location. 

If you have any questions, please reach out to your HR representative.

EnterpriseProperties.Comments: This is the Employee Handbook for employees working in Finland.
